_sText:
This map is for the j2 Halloween Mappack. See the other maps here:
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/36702
Check them out! They own.

This map is not big. Not ideal if you want to play with a lot of players but it can hold 32 players in total. Don't be afraid to explore every corner of the house: there is only one (quite obvious) deathtrap anyways.

NOTE! I was told that this map could crash if played with more than +/- 20 people. This has only happened on one server and it's not confirmed, but you're warned.
I would like to thank the guys at http://www.sovereign-forces.com for supporting the j2 mappers.

Have fun!
Miles 
"Dr.Boo"
